Tour de Cure Red Riders

   You are why we ride! We celebrate everyone who lives with type 1 and
   type 2 diabetes as our heroes on the day of the event. If you have
   diabetes, join our community of riders!

   [11]Find out how to become a Red Rider today!


Tour de Cure Multi-Day Events

   [12]Tour de Cure: New England Classic

   The New England Classic Tour de Cure offers a 2-day or 7-day adventure
   through the picturesque towns, coastlines and mountains of several
   northern states. Click [13]here to learn more

Tour de Cure for Women

   [14]Tour de Cure: Women's Series Logo

   Ride in our Women's Series event in Northern California. For more
   information and to register: [15]diabetes.org/womenstour

